===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*deyḱ-}}
From {{der|en|enm|condicioun}}, from {{der|en|fro|condicion}} (French {{m|fr|condition}}), from {{der|en|la|condicio}}. Unetymological change in spelling due to confusion with {{m|la|conditio}}.

